posts.name: Ronin
posts.cooked:
What are some of your favorite (or least favorite) noises or reactions to hear during comps, build season, load in/out, etc.?

I’m partial to the “Oh!” from the crowd whenever a robot tips or the sound that Kraken’s make whenever they stall. It’s become a running joke on my team that we’ll be “cool” when our robot whines too!

posts.name: Elliot S
posts.cooked:
L0ading:

I’m partial to the “Oh!” from the crowd whenever a robot tips or the sound that Kraken’s make whenever they stall. It’s become a running joke on my team that we’ll be “cool” when our robot whines too!

And then the cheer if they can right themselves, or even better when their partner helps them do it!

2910 doing a somersault at IRI in 2023 is pretty crazy:

Does “weirdly loud music” count as one sound for least favorite? As for favorite, I think that the field fault sound is almost mocking the teams playing which kind of represents everyone’s emotions at that point.
